ZH: 蜜蜂是非常勤劳的昆虫。
EN: Bees are very hardworking insects.

ZH: 我们家后院里有许多蜜蜂。
EN: There are many bees in the backyard of our house.

ZH: 蜜蜂传粉，促进植物生长。
EN: Bees pollinate and promote plant growth.

ZH: 蜜蜂的蜂蜜是一种天然的甜味剂。
EN: Bee honey is a natural sweetener.

ZH: 小心被蜜蜂蛰到。
EN: Be careful not to get stung by a bee.

ZH: 蜜蜂可以制造蜂蜜和蜂蜡。
EN: Bees can produce honey and beeswax.

ZH: 蜜蜂是地球上最重要的传粉工作者之一。
EN: Bees are one of the most important pollinators on Earth.

ZH: 蜜蜂队伍里有工蜂，蜂王和雄蜂。
EN: A bee colony consists of worker bees, a queen bee, and drones.

ZH: 蜜蜂是社会性昆虫。
EN: Bees are social insects.

ZH: 蜜蜂对农作物产生积极影响。
EN: Bees have a positive impact on crop production.

ZH: 蜜蜂在花朵间来回忙碌着。
EN: Bees buzz back and forth between flowers.

ZH: 蜜蜂的蜇刺含有少量毒素。
EN: The sting of a bee contains a small amount of venom.

ZH: 如果你患有蜜蜂过敏症，要小心被蜜蜂蛰到。
EN: If you have a bee allergy, be careful not to get stung by a bee.

ZH: 蜜蜂巢是由蜂蜡和蜂巢纸构成。
EN: A bee hive is made of beeswax and honeycomb paper.

ZH: 蜜蜂通过震动表达方向信息。
EN: Bees communicate direction through vibrations.

ZH: 蜜蜂能在迷失时找回蜂巢的位置。
EN: Bees can find their way back to the hive even when lost.

ZH: 蜜蜂以花粉和蜂蜜为食。
EN: Bees feed on pollen and honey.

ZH: 蜜蜂的蜂蜜具有抗生素和抗氧化特性。
EN: Bee honey has antibiotic and antioxidant properties.

ZH: 蜜蜂在冬季会囤存足够的花蜜。
EN: Bees store enough honey for the winter.
